- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep neural networks and reinforcement learning to design the networked controller, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses deep neural networks to design the networked controller, which falls under the category of neural computing. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): Although the paper does not explicitly mention robotics, the concept of networked control can be applied to robotics, and the use of deep neural networks and reinforcement learning is relevant to robotics applications.
